column1: Note:1.Figures before and of 1981 are from household registrations; for years of 1982,1990,2000, 2010 and 2020 are the census year estimates;and figures for the rest of years are estimated on the basis of the annual national sample survey of population.
¡¡¡¡¡¡2.Total population and population by gender include the servicemen of the Chinese People''s Liberation Army, who are classified as urban population in population by residence.
